link readline library to compiler command

If you don't add the readline library during compilation you will get
undefined reference to 'readline' error.

for the linker to find definition of the readline() function during the linking phase,
ensure that you are linking Readline library ('libreadline') when compiling
your program.
Add -lreadline to  your compile command

cc *.c -lreadline

